fields.title: Two Sum
fields.description: Given an array of integers, return indices of the two numbers such that they add up to a specific target.

fields.title: Best Time to Buy and Sell Stock
fields.description: You are given an array prices where prices[i] is the price of a given stock on the ith day. Find the maximum profit.

fields.title: Contains Duplicate
fields.description: Given an array of integers, find if the array contains any duplicates.

fields.title: Product of Array Except Self
fields.description: Given an array nums of n integers where n > 1, return an array output such that output[i] is equal to the product of all the elements of nums except nums[i].

fields.title: Maximum Subarray
fields.description: Given an integer array nums, find the contiguous subarray (containing at least one number) which has the largest sum and return its sum.

fields.title: Maximum Product Subarray
fields.description: Given an integer array nums, find the contiguous subarray within an array (containing at least one number) which has the largest product.

fields.title: Find Minimum in Rotated Sorted Array
fields.description: Suppose an array sorted in ascending order is rotated at some pivot unknown to you beforehand. Find the minimum element.

fields.title: Search in Rotated Sorted Array
fields.description: You are given an integer array nums sorted in ascending order, and an integer target. Suppose that nums is rotated at some pivot unknown to you beforehand. Search for the target.

fields.title: 3Sum
fields.description: Given an array nums of n integers, are there elements a, b, c in nums such that a + b + c = 0? Find all unique triplets in the array which gives the sum of zero.

fields.title: Container With Most Water
fields.description: Given n non-negative integers a1, a2, ..., an , where each represents a point at coordinate (i, ai). n vertical lines are drawn such that the two endpoints of the line i is at (i, ai) and (i, 0). Find two lines, which together with the x-axis forms a container, such that the container contains the most water.

fields.title: Sum of Two Integers
fields.description: Given two integers a and b, return the sum of the two integers without using the operators + and -.

fields.title: Number of 1 Bits
fields.description: Write a function that takes an unsigned integer and returns the number of '1' bits it has (also known as the Hamming weight).

fields.title: Counting Bits
fields.description: Given a non-negative integer num. For every numbers i in the range 0 ≤ i ≤ num calculate the number of 1's in their binary representation and return them as an array.

fields.title: Missing Number
fields.description: Given an array nums containing n distinct numbers in the range [0, n], return the only number in the range that is missing from the array.

fields.title: Reverse Bits
fields.description: Reverse bits of a given 32 bits unsigned integer.

fields.title: Climbing Stairs
fields.description: You are climbing a staircase. It takes n steps to reach the top. Each time you can either climb 1 or 2 steps. In how many distinct ways can you climb to the top?

fields.title: Coin Change
fields.description: You are given coins of different denominations and a total amount of money amount. Write a function to compute the fewest number of coins that you need to make up that amount.

fields.title: Longest Increasing Subsequence
fields.description: Given an integer array nums, return the length of the longest strictly increasing subsequence.

fields.title: Longest Common Subsequence
fields.description: Given two strings text1 and text2, return the length of their longest common subsequence.

fields.title: Word Break
fields.description: Given a string s and a dictionary of strings wordDict, return true if s can be segmented into a space-separated sequence of one or more dictionary words.
